Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Kansas Driver’s License Practice Test is intended to assist you with preparing for the Kansas Driver License exam. Please note that this is skill is only provided as a tool to assist you with preparing for the exam and is not a driver education training program. For more information about the Kansas Driver Examination please visit www.ksrevenue.org. To use this skill please listen to each question carefully. Provide your answer after each question is posed. To repeat a question please say “repeat”. At the end of the practice exam, your score will be provided. This practice exam may not include questions that require the user to review a picture. Please visit www.ksrevenue.org for sample questions that include pictures.

The Kansas Driver’s License Practice Test skill is provided for educational purposes only. This is not a driver education program. This skill may not include questions that require the user to review a picture. Please visit www.ksrevenue.org for more information about the Kansas Driver Examination and to see complete list of questions, go to: https://www.ksrevenue.org/pdf/dlhb.pdf
